    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Boozy Bailey’s Cheesecake. A British home-cook's dish — the kind of recipe families adjust across generations. Adjustable for what you need."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Cake batters reward weighing over scooping. Room-temperature butter and eggs, raised properly, tested with a skewer."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
